## About The Project

<p>
The project was developed in a team, our team is called The Recruitables. The project consists of Functional Tests, which tests a webshop called SwagLabs. This site is specifically designed to train testers, so some bugs have been introduced into the site. The site itself can be found at this address: 
<a href="https://www.saucedemo.com/" >https://www.saucedemo.com/ </a>

</p>
